title: Dwyane Wade
description:
In this episode Ellen sits down with basketball superstar Dwyane Wade, who is a three-time NBA Champion, thirteen-time NBA All-Star, and Olympic gold medalist. He and Ellen discuss fatherhood, leading with love, and his new book Dwyane, a photographic memoir.
